question: What café is available on the route to SEA LIFE Minnesota Aquarium, Bloomington, MN within a 120 kilometers radius from Water Street Inn, Stillwater, MN?
sql:
WITH
    angle AS (SELECT degrees(ST_Azimuth(ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-92.805004 45.056347)',4326)::geography, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-93.240076 44.854752)',4326)::geography)) AS value)
SELECT * FROM pois,angle
WHERE amenity = 'cafe'
AND ST_DWithin(pois.geometry, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-92.805004 45.056347)',4326)::geography, 120000)
AND (degrees(ST_Azimuth(ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-92.805004 45.056347)',4326)::geography, pois.geometry)) BETWEEN angle.value - 22.5 AND angle.value + 22.5);
